keyFacts: A complaint was received by a DHS Attaché in Vienna pertaining to individuals referenced in the FBI's Epstein investigation (case 50D-NY-3027571).
The FBI Legal Attaché for Austria, Croatia, and Slovenia forwarded this complaint to the NYC FBI team for follow-up.
The email demonstrates international coordination between U.S. law enforcement agencies (FBI and DHS) regarding the Epstein investigation as of March 2020.
